hinking you can get away with flaming friends of mine like Nila because she's too good to respond in kind is a big mistake to make.  I'm so pissed to see this shit-stirring bs that I'm swearing in the post.<br><br><br>nodda<br><br> <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#FFFFFF><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub28.ezboard.com/utatianaefatecaster.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Tatianae Fatecaster</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 406<br> <font color=#FF0000>(4/22/01 6:44:34 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub28.ezboard.com/fdrinal28133frm12.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=166.topic&index=6>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   ..</span><hr size=1> A) You wrote more than 1 paragraph and that is not legal here.<br><br>B) He thinks men are the superior race to women, and clearly has issues with women as a result. He is serious about this, and struggles to comprehend anything anotherwise.<br><br>C) I believe every one of those weird &quot;stalking&quot; stories I have seen other women write about him in here. Basis the whole 2 conversations I had with him, he apparently does live his life fully in the fantasy world and takes his relationships in EQ very seriously. He talked **extensively** of love lost etc. and for a while I thought he was talking about a real life person, but it was EQ. He did not even know me when he began the conversation and it was very misplaced.<br><br><br>With that information, I  assume that he is fairly insecure, probably not social in real life, and probably not well grounded in the outside world and true relationships. Use that information draw your own conclusions, but I usually just skim his posts and try to avoid flaming him because most of the time I feel sorry for him.<br><br>RE: Sutekh I have had 2 encounters with him, one as a newbie, and one through this web board. Those brief encounters 